{"id":540225,"date":[{"year":1974,"month":11,"day":17}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"","genre":"","count":"298","ytitle":"","mtitle":"炉火熊熊","ftitle":"","authors":["钱国梁"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华船厂　钱国梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呵，炉火熊熊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光闪闪，风呼呼，一派喧腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟霞万朵在这里卷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈焰千度在这里喷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵呵，就是这时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱打开通红的炉门。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打铁，抢火候呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快!快!展开新的进攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢钳，炉火中冲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻件，炉火中蹦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火的大旗呵，哗啦啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火的战歌呵，轰隆隆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那硬铮铮的锤头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓足气，不倦地冲锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挟住钢铁的雷霆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召唤鲜红的风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铿铿铿，豪迈的宣告——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"趁热打铁才能成功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铿铿，越锻劲越猛!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铿铿，越锻骨越硬!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，这炉火熊熊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们锤炼成革命的英雄!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢——热火火地耀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渣——灰溜溜地滚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好呵，炉火熊熊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧得更旺呵烧得更猛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，当今通红的时代呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这么个大好时辰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锻吧!在人民革命的锤头下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新世界呵，正在锻成!"}]}